---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<div class="bg-powder-blue/5">
  <Container>
    <div class="py-8 text-xl">
      <div class="md:grid grid-cols-3 md:mb-5">
        <h2
          class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gun-metal mb-2 md:ml-4 md:leading-[3rem] col-span-1"
        >
          Our contemporary facilities offer a safe haven for growth and
          development.
        </h2>
        <div class="md:w-3/3 col-span-2">
          <p class="text-gun-metal-light md:text-xl mb-2">
            At Harbour Light, young people's welfare is our priority. Our
            experienced team, with backgrounds in supported living, business,
            and youth projects, listens to and respects their rights and
            aspirations, providing a nurturing environment.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gun-metal-light md:text-xl mb-2">
            Through our unique tailor made programs, we help young people build
            support networks and vital life skills, fostering confidence for
            their future. Acknowledging diverse backgrounds, we empower young
            people to overcome low self-esteem, encouraging positive choices and
            aspirations. Our advocacy extends to helping them access independent
            support services and seize opportunities for personal growth and
            success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
